There would be no hope in this situation, even for&nbsp;
the most well-suited army, much less millions of&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:46:08.000 --> 00:46:13.520
slaves and runaways on foot. "What is the sound&nbsp;
we hear behind us? We cried to the Lord to bring&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:46:13.520 --> 00:46:19.520
us out of Egypt, and here we are looking at&nbsp;
