00:48:16.880 --> 00:48:22.000
The reason I wanted you to see that today&nbsp;
is because the children of Israel had no&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:48:22.000 --> 00:48:28.000
point of reference for this Red Sea, had no&nbsp;
way of knowing how God was going to do it.

00:48:28.000 --> 00:48:33.120
Maybe you don't either, and you're standing there&nbsp;
